cme.control
Class BusDepotControl

java.lang.Object
  cme.control.BusDepotControl
Direct Known Subclasses:
BusStopControl, DepotControl
public abstract class BusDepotControl
extends java.lang.Object

BusDepotControl includes functions and validations of bus stops/depots.The 2 main functions are adding and deleting of bus stops/depots with validations on the map.

Author:
Lai Sze Chuan

cursorY - the y coordinate of the mouse click
Returns:
